- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper discusses the development of a flight control firmware for unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs), which falls under the domain of robotics. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper focuses on the development of a flight control system for UAVs, which falls under the domain of systems and control. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper introduces the use of neural networks for flight control, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses the use of neural networks for flight control, which falls under the domain of artificial intelligence. 
- cs.EM (Embedded Systems): The paper discusses the implementation of the flight control firmware on embedded hardware, which falls under the domain of embedded systems.
